<HEADLINE>
<P>
LAS VEGAS FIRM TO DO ROAD REPAIRS NEAR HOOVER DAM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The U.S. Bureau of Reclamation has awarded a $4.7-million contract for road 
realignment at Hoover Dam to Frehner Construction Co. of Las Vegas, government 
officials said. The project will include straightening a portion of U.S. 
Highway 93 adjacent to Hoover Dam in Nevada. 
</P>
<P>
When complete, the highway will be safer and provided more direct access to the 
future Hoover Dam visitor's center. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
